@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bptaea(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v2
    v1 = (v0 * (wp.exp(v2 + 0.24) / (v1 + 0.35 + v1 + 0.34)))
    v2 = (tmp - wp.abs(0.33))
    tmp = (v0 - ((v0 + 0.33 * tmp + 0.49) / tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
